title: Single-source Claude plugin capability inventory docs
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: Claude plugin capability inventory is duplicated and already drifting between docs/CLAUDE_CODE_PLUGIN.md:45-83 and plugins/pm-claude/README.md:5-14 plus :101-174. The docs repeat counts and inventories for MCP tools, skills, slash commands, subagents, install modes, and pm_run actions. Current drift: docs/CLAUDE_CODE_PLUGIN.md:83 says 9 slash commands, while plugins/pm-claude/README.md:11 says 14; plugins/pm-claude/README.md:12 says 3 subagents but lists 4. Existing pm-rjgh covers PRD/CHANGELOG/marketplace/AGENTS hygiene and pm-js0r covers wrapper/smoke code, not this docs inventory drift."
